# Create a free AWS Skillbuilder Account
#### [Made by Tasha Penwell with Scribe](https://scribehow.com/shared/Create_a_free_AWS_Skillbuilder_Account__XwK21XnGS7-1cVu0DyJRCg)
This guide provides step-by-step instructions on how to create a free AWS Skillbuilder account. By following these steps, users can gain access to the Skillbuilder platform and start exploring the various resources and learning materials available.

1\. Go to <https://explore.skillbuilder.aws/pages/16/learner-dashboard> and select **Sign In to Skill Builder**. (The next step will prompt you to sign up if you do not have an account yet.) 

![](https://ajeuwbhvhr.cloudimg.io/colony-recorder.s3.amazonaws.com/files/2024-04-09/70aaad57-9f9b-449c-a164-343c27bae823/ascreenshot.jpeg?tl_px=0,0&br_px=2704,1756&force_format=png&width=1120.0&wat=1&wat_opacity=0.7&wat_gravity=northwest&wat_url=https://colony-recorder.s3.us-west-1.amazonaws.com/images/watermarks/FB923C_standard.png&wat_pad=612,398)


2\. Select **Create or Sign In**

![](https://ajeuwbhvhr.cloudimg.io/colony-recorder.s3.amazonaws.com/files/2024-04-09/ea3dede2-3cb2-4049-8174-e75384af073f/user_cropped_screenshot.jpeg?tl_px=410,83&br_px=2704,1364&force_format=png&width=1120.0&wat=1&wat_opacity=0.7&wat_gravity=northwest&wat_url=https://colony-recorder.s3.us-west-1.amazonaws.com/images/watermarks/FB923C_standard.png&wat_pad=684,277)


3\. Enter your email address

![](https://ajeuwbhvhr.cloudimg.io/colony-recorder.s3.amazonaws.com/files/2024-04-09/deaf936a-aafa-4a88-b4f7-1ad9f8def99c/ascreenshot.jpeg?tl_px=608,757&br_px=2328,1718&force_format=png&width=1120.0&wat=1&wat_opacity=0.7&wat_gravity=northwest&wat_url=https://colony-recorder.s3.us-west-1.amazonaws.com/images/watermarks/FB923C_standard.png&wat_pad=524,276)


4\. Add your name and select **Next.**

![](https://ajeuwbhvhr.cloudimg.io/colony-recorder.s3.amazonaws.com/files/2024-04-09/5e873e19-087c-42dd-9e26-dfb4b6d51701/ascreenshot.jpeg?tl_px=642,794&br_px=2362,1756&force_format=png&width=1120.0&wat=1&wat_opacity=0.7&wat_gravity=northwest&wat_url=https://colony-recorder.s3.us-west-1.amazonaws.com/images/watermarks/FB923C_standard.png&wat_pad=524,369)


5\. Check your email and enter the verification code. If you do not see it in your email, follow the tips below.

- Check your spam folder
- Wait at least five minutes and refresh your email page

![](https://ajeuwbhvhr.cloudimg.io/colony-recorder.s3.amazonaws.com/files/2024-04-09/1398f2cc-52cf-41b8-9957-bcd9bfb5c043/screenshot.jpeg?tl_px=148,275&br_px=1524,1044&force_format=png&width=1120.0)


6\. Once you have verified your email, you can now begin exploring AWS Skillbuilder. 
